$. Finally,\nwe show that the class of mixtures of $k$ log-concave distributions over\n$\\mathbb{R}^d$ is PAC-learnable using\n$\\widetilde{O}(d^{(d+5)/2}\\epsilon^{-(d+9)/2}k)$ samples.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 6 Jun 2017 03:47:28 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 17 Sep 2017 17:12:36 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 3 Jun 2018 18:58:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-06-05"}
