$. In passing we show that for any separable Banach spaces $E,F$, any\n$w^*$-measurable esssentially bounded function valued in the Banach space\n$\\Gamma_2(E,F^*)$ of operators from $E$ into $F^*$ factoring through Hilbert\nspace admits a $w^*$-measurable Hilbert space factorization.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 6 Jun 2017 08:59:50 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 25 Jan 2019 07:41:21 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 8 Jul 2020 09:43:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-07-09"}
